不親民，被認為是花<br />\n錢當盤子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics.ettoday.net/images/5478/5478313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5478%2F5478313.jpg&h=cb19be21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://health.ettoday.net/news/1928871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1928871&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=406ca115\" target=\"_blank\">https://health.ettoday.net/news/1928871</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"只睇許藍方博士<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCsc1dZtJfAsWegx-Ri7BElw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCsc1dZtJfAsWegx-Ri7BElw&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=69b41e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCsc1dZtJfAsWegx-Ri7BElw</a>"},{"pid":"398fbe7e0f7fd1f5000db6bb1c9a986021e5520d","tid":2429014,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"iherb大撚把 又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ac7c9319fb31d1280bd50f538df407d5caa739","tid":2429014,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"437d9fba28bda22f46be567dc9073f8a4ac291a4","tid":2429014,"uid":375135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91ea340462f7ca614813dd8bd6a5608ef55522a4","tid":2429014,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pics.ettoday.net/images/5478/d5478286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5478%2Fd5478286.jpg&h=13a3e82a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網紅理科太太透過募資平台販售綜合維他命，將各種營養品如維生素、鐵、DHA、Q10等通<br />\n通濃縮成一小顆膠囊，等於吃一瓶強抵十二瓶，引發熱議！有醫師表示，該款產品製作者<br />\n完全是大外行，裡頭的營養成分劑量少到不可思議，「吃外面一顆B群，可抵48顆太X膠囊<br />\n」，充其量只能算是安慰劑而已。<br />\n <br />\n知名網紅理科太太及生醫團隊在平台募資的綜合維他命膠囊，而擁有減肥、腸道專長的家<br />\